  "3315230": {
    "name": "Rocket Squad: Infinity",
    "steam_appid": 3315230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为了宇宙的和平与秩序！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Rocket Squad》是一款团队合作的第一人称射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入充满危险的星球，收集资源，并安全返回你的避难所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用每位角色的独特能力，策略性地组建你的队伍，恢复宇宙的秩序。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/48aa25c70a18dd879b916ad7845dd6c7.avif?t=1748590039\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras_big/48aa25c70a18dd879b916ad7845dd6c7.avif?t=1748590039 width=800 height=326 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特工</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色都有独特的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分析他们的优势，策略性地组建你的团队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/4f8069b44c33a14cce5b39fe739f13a3.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/4f8069b44c33a14cce5b39fe739f13a3.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/4f8069b44c33a14cce5b39fe739f13a3.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>预算管理</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个行动都需要经费，资源不足会严重影响任务执行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请在每次行动前后认真管理财务，合理使用团队预算，避免浪费。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高效的财务管理是通往胜利的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/67a7c89723b314d5e98810416db58344.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/67a7c89723b314d5e98810416db58344.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/67a7c89723b314d5e98810416db58344.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>球渗透</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宇宙的经济秩序已经崩溃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限量子核心的开发使无限加密货币挖掘成为可能，导致了这场灾难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入危险的星球，恢复宇宙的和平与秩序。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/17ef4e610cf0a5aea34130a66cc0d98d.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/17ef4e610cf0a5aea34130a66cc0d98d.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/17ef4e610cf0a5aea34130a66cc0d98d.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与机器人战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机器人垄断了无限量子核心，摧毁了宇宙的经济。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们已不再只是简单的机器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与这些富有的机器人作战，它们已成为宇宙的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/2d1ff238658e55ccf15eb348bba20582.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/2d1ff238658e55ccf15eb348bba20582.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/2d1ff238658e55ccf15eb348bba20582.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经济复苏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取珍贵物品，并安全撤离。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掠夺富裕机器人的金库，拯救濒临崩溃的宇宙未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/ad4d3c21bbeb0815cc9a97e47d443d84.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/ad4d3c21bbeb0815cc9a97e47d443d84.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/ad4d3c21bbeb0815cc9a97e47d443d84.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家强化</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用各种神器提升角色能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭配适合角色特点的神器，打造属于你的独特游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/b20ca1608dc9bc110f813a0e7be4164d.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/b20ca1608dc9bc110f813a0e7be4164d.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/b20ca1608dc9bc110f813a0e7be4164d.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>避难所装饰</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的避难所是你的安全之家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种家具和装饰品，自由装扮，让它成为真正属于你的空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/eb39b3fba2a7e99b389d896b6bb455fe.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/eb39b3fba2a7e99b389d896b6bb455fe.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/eb39b3fba2a7e99b389d896b6bb455fe.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多人模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多 4 名好友组队，一起拯救宇宙！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/1e6d0d95069374c8ce807a5529ea75aa.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/1e6d0d95069374c8ce807a5529ea75aa.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/1e6d0d95069374c8ce807a5529ea75aa.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
